                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">Purificador Consul / Electrolux</p>
                <p class="text-2xl font-black text-orange-500">R$ 0,05</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">por litro filtrado</p>
