              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden group">
              <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-slate-800 bg-white hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors list-none">
                Qual a diferença entre purificador refrigerado e não refrigerado?
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
